\subtree{
\title{GF(3) conservation}
\taxon{remark}

\p{The 19 skills partition as 6(+1) + 6(0) + 7(-1). The sum is
#{6 - 7 = -1 \equiv 2 \pmod{3}}. To restore balance, the next hatchery
skill should be trit +1 or 0.}
}
